snippet.title: Star Revenge 2: Night of Doom - Bob-omb's Sand Valley [No Save States]
snippet.description:
Star Revenge 2: Night of Doom is an SM64 ROM hack made by BroDute.

Timestamps:
Star 1: Big Bob-omb's Sand Problem (0:00)
Star 2: Back to the Pillars (1:43)
Star 3: Good Timed Walljumps (2:30)
Star 4 + 100 Coins: Find the 12 Red Coins (3:09)
Star 5: 5 Magically !-Boxes (8:00)
Star 6: Somewhere Over the Quicksand (10:30)

Well, it's been almost a year since I uploaded the old version of this video. I've decided I'm redoing this walkthrough, because the old version was practically unwatchable due to the amount of lag. Besides, it will be a good practice for 152 star runs.

This video is more than twice as short now, and there's plenty of reasons for that, such as the lack of lag, combining red coins and 100 coins this time, and the discoveries of many new strategies.
